snippet: Serena Williams expects her sister Venus to be back at Melbourne Park next year for a 17th crack at winning the Australian Open, the American world number one said on Wednesday....
lead_paragraph: Serena Williams expects her sister Venus to be back at Melbourne Park next year for a 17th crack at winning the Australian Open, the American world number one said on Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: Serena Expects Venus to Be Back in Melbourne Next Year
headline.main: Serena Expects Venus to Be Back in Melbourne Next Year
